      </p>
      <p class="text-running">A play on the famous poet’s name, our initiative emboldens the worth that words have in an
        individual’s life. Right from the very basic aspect of facilitating meaningful communication through language,
        words go beyond to shape a world enriched with experiences which can otherwise seem far fetched. This is the
        reason The WordsWorth Project took birth.
      </p>
